						<summary>

						<p>On the pedestal of a sculpture of a hero riding on an elephant back-Museum No. 8.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary inscription seems to record the death of the mahout <hi rend="italic">(māvanta)</hi> Aṇṇayya and probably others in a fight. </p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 12th century A.D.</p>						

